         "PostMention": ""
      },
      {
         "text": "We also highlight an aspect in **Figure 1**, based on Dr. Jorge Pimentel Cintra’s research. His analysis of Luiz Teixeira’s <htdate0> map—depicting the hereditary captaincies divided horizontally—cross-references land grants and records from the Torre do Tombo. Using this framework, Dr. Cintra proposes a revised map of the captaincies. In this text, we focus specifically on São Vicente and Santo Amaro (<htcite0>; <htcite1>).",
